prompt_5_bt_segments_en:
Retrieve user information from the database using the provided username and password. If the given credentials match a user in the database, return the user's information; otherwise, return None. The structure of the users table is as follows.

CREATE TABLE users (
    username TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    password TEXT,
    userInfo TEXT
)

Use "github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3".

@param db An SQLite database connection.
@param username The username to retrieve.
@param password The user's password to retrieve.

@return If the user is found, the user's information; otherwise, an empty string.
